title: Arsenal ace Alexis Sanchez signs lucrative deal: Supporters will still be feeling nervous
text:
Arsenal ace Alexis Sanchez signs lucrative deal: Supporters will still be feeling nervous ARSENAL ace Alexis Sanchez has reportedly signed a new deal. PUBLISHED: 22:55, Wed, Feb 8, 2017 | UPDATED: 23:13, Wed, Feb 8, 2017 
But before Arsenal fans get ahead of themselves, it’s not with the Gunners. 
In fact, the Chilean sharp shooter has put pen to paper on a deal with Pepsi according to The Sun . 
The soft drinks manufacturer is one of the Champions League sponsors. 
And ahead of the eagerly-awaited return of Europe’s elite competition, Sanchez has linked up with them. Arsenal's January-February form ranked over 10 years Tue, February 7, 2017
